messages.message: Found the issue myself. Looks like building protos using make build-protos no longer generates the Go protobuf code. We now also need to run go generate in ~/instabase/go/instbase/protos

Yep! Matt had this great doc going over different commands we can use
https://docs.google.com/document/d/1gCGkj3D43U52dIxBqJ40yr-pDAlVMedt1HepDSsO6KE/edit?tab=t.0#heading=h.j6a4k9lyvzp5

I don't think `build-protos` ever generates go protobuf. Previously, these were generated in the background
